<h1>New Wiki</h1>
 
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <p>Guidelines for wikis</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Don't just make stuff up! We'll find out.</li>
      <li>Keep it PG-13.</li>
      <li>No Pepe memes. Talking about Pepe will result in an automatic ban.</li>
      <li>NEW FEATURE: PREMIUM USERS may now add COLLABORATORS to their wikis! Just click the "Edit" button after you've created your wiki to be taken to the form to add collaborators!</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <%= form_for @wiki do |f| %>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.label :title %>
        <%= f.text_field :title, class: 'form-control', placeholder: "Enter wiki title" %>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.label :body %>
        <%= f.text_area :body, rows: 8, class: 'form-control', placeholder: "Enter wiki body" %>
      </div>

    <%= render "wikis/form", f: f %>

      <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.submit "Save", class: 'btn btn-success' %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>